QD Strategic cooperation with Minsheng Bank is yet another move from the management to increase shareholder value It is not a founding partnership its much more important QD is providing high deep value tech which means that the already minuscule multiple is going thru the roof They are moving from a risky financial sector business with its own valuation metrics towards software valuation In addition to providing software for big banks they are already building a simple plug and play financial service for other apps in order to help them monetize Higher valuation less risk profits Where else can we find this
